## Error 2: Missing permissions

Cause:
GitHub App permissions not set

Fix:

* Pull Requests → Read & Write
* Checks → Read & Write

---

## Error 3: GitHub App not installed

Fix:
Install App under GitHub settings

---

## Error 4: OAuth not configured

Fix:
Create OAuth App and configure in SonarQube

